SUMMARY:Art Making for All: Winter Wonderlands
DESCRIPTION:Approach the seasonal glow of winter with a special eye on 
 seeing patterns\, colors and beauty in the landscape of seasons change. 
 This workshop engages everyone in the surrounding natural beauty of Durham 
 and the western mountains. This workshop will demonstrate and allow 
 participants to increase their techniques and skills while exploring 
 practices of being outside and respectfully aware of nature during the 
 season. This is an intergenerational program--all are welcome! All supplies 
 will be provided. Please register.
