 sooner or later\, “How do I price my product or service?” This 
 90-minute workshop is designed to help small business owners and startups 
 effectively price their products or services. Taught by Fares Khalidi\, 
 this workshop will help your clients learn how to calculate costs\, 
 research competitors\, understand customer value\, and choose a suitable 
 pricing strategy.
