SUMMARY:Friends of the Durham Library Pop-Up DVD Sale
DESCRIPTION:Join the Friends of the Durham Library at Main Library for one 
 of their famous pop-up DVD sales! The Friends will have thousands of 
 movies\, TV shows\, children's educational shows\, and countless other 
 genres available\, all at the rock-bottom price of $1 each. There will be 
 box sets available\, priced at just $1 per disc\, as well as a smaller 
 selection of puzzles and games priced from $3. The best part is that every 
 dollar you spend goes directly back to supporting library staff through 
 programming grants\, continuing education scholarships\, and other forms of 
 morale-boosting support.
