SUMMARY:One Seed One Community Packing Party!
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our first One Seed One Community packing party! 
 Pack seeds and meet new people.\n\nOne Seed One Community is an annual 
 program that offers free seeds\, community connection\, and the experience 
