SUMMARY:Preschool STEAM Storytime: Let's Learn About Time!
DESCRIPTION:Preschoolers (ages 3-5 years) and their caregivers are welcome 
 to join Ms. Natalie for a STEAM (Science\, Technology\, Engineering\, 
 Arts\, and Mathematics) storytime! On the 1st and 3rd Monday of every 
 month\, we will explore a different STEAM topic with stories\, songs\, and 
 a hands-on activity.\n\nThis week\, we will learn all about time and create 
 our own clocks using paper plates\, cardstock paper\, crayons\, markers\, 
 and brass fasteners!\n\nRegistration is required.\n\nIf you have any 
 questions\, please contact us @ 919-560-8592.
