SUMMARY:***CANCELED DUE TO INCLEMENT WEATHER***- Kidney Smart Education Class
DESCRIPTION:Join Meghan Killmond\, BS\, MS\, CCHT to learn about kidney 
 health!\n\nClasses are available to anyone interested in learning more 
 about Chronic Kidney Disease(CKD) at no cost.\n\nYou will learn:\n\nThe 
 role of the kidneys What causes kidney disease What kidney diet resources 
 are available What can be done to manage a healthy lifestyle How medication 
 management can lead to better kidney health Why employment and insurance 
 coverage are important What treatment options are available How the 
 transplant process works
LOCATION:Conference Room #3214\, Main Library (300 N. Roxboro St)
