DESCRIPTION:Gain valuable computer skills on these topics:\n\nComputer 
 Basics\n\n\n	Using an operating system\; opening programs\; saving\, 
 copying\, and deleting files.\n\n\nDocuments & Typing\n\n\n	Word processing 
 basics\; editing and saving documents\; formatting text\; cut copy and 
 paste.\n\n\nInternet Basics \n\n\n	Browsing websites\; searching with 
 Google\; using online forms\; keeping accounts secure.\n\n\nOnline 
 Life\n\n\n	Avoiding scams\; protecting your privacy\; finding reliable 
 info\; using social media safely.\n\n\nTo sign up: Call 919-293-1133 or 
 click the link to register below:\n\nEnglish Registration Link\n
