SUMMARY:Preschool Process Art: Tape Resist Art
DESCRIPTION:Children ages 2-5 are invited to join Ms. Kristen and get 
 creative! Process art is child-directed and embraces the process of 
 creating\, rather than the end result. \n\nThis week\, we'll make geometric 
 prints using painters tape\, watercolor paints\, and cardstock. 
 \n\nRegistration is appreciated\, but not required. Please dress for a 
 mess. Can't wait to see what you create! \n\n
