SUMMARY:Fix-a-Leak Week: Fun with Water Science
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars for EPA's annual Fix a Leak Week\, March 16 
 through 22\, 2026.\n\nDid you know household leaks can waste nearly 1 
 trillion gallons of water annually nationwide? Each year the Durham’s 
 Department of Water Management takes part in the EPA’s campaign to hunt 
 down the drips during Fix a Leak Week. Join the water efficiency experts on 
 Saturday\, March 21st for a fun water activity and learn how to be a leak 
 detective. Registration encouraged for each participant.
LOCATION:Innovation Lab\, Main Library (300 N. Roxboro St)
ORGANIZER;CN="Christina Economou":MAILTO:ceconomou@dconc.gov
