 pretty posies or vibrant violets.  The choice will be yours!  Contact 
 Dominique at fdiggs@dconc.gov if you have any questions\, concerns\, or 
 need any accommodations.\n\nThis is a systemwide event brought to you by 
 the Teen Services Committee. For the month of March we have decided to 
 focus on learning how to read recipes and food. These programs are for 
 tweens\, teens\, and emerging adults. More information can be found about 
 each program by visiting the library website.
LOCATION:North Regional - Children's Programming Room\, North Regional Library (221 Milton Rd)
ORGANIZER;CN="Dominique Diggs":MAILTO:fdiggs@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:
UID:LibCal-14288-16408321
URL:https://durhamcountylibrary.libcal.com/event/16408321
