 schedule below:\n\nMonday\, February 16: Excel Basics\nMonday\, February 
 23: Drop-In Tech Help\nMonday\, March 2: PowerPoint Basics \nMonday\, March 
 9: Drop-in Tech Help\nMonday\, March 23: Organize Your Photos\, Files\, & 
 More\nMonday\, March 30: Drop-in Tech Help\nMonday\, April 6: AI Basics
