SUMMARY:CANCELLED | Ready\, Set\, Baby (Spanish) at East Regional
DESCRIPTION:CANCELLED DUE TO LACK OF REGISTRATIONS.\n\nReady\, Set\, Baby 
 Classes:  Free prenatal breastfeeding education class designed to help you 
 get ready for your baby\, whether you are a first-time parent or adding to 
 your family. These classes are a great way to prepare for pregnancy\, 
 birth\, and life with a newborn. You’ll get helpful information on 
 breastfeeding\, postpartum care\, and what to expect in those early weeks. 
 Our class is packed with conversations\, resources\, and a raffle prize at 
 the end! You’ll have a chance to win amazing prizes like:\n\n\n	Breast 
 pumps\n	Diaper bags filled with baby essentials\n	Car seats\n	Breastfeeding 
 pillows\n	…and more! \n\n\nRegistration required. Questions? Please 
 contact Jasmine at jjohnson@dconc.gov. \n\n \n\nCan't make it to this 
 location? These classes will be held at all Durham County locations over 
 the next couple of months. See the flyer below for the upcoming dates at 
 the other locations!
LOCATION:East Regional - Children's Programming Room\, East Regional Library (211 Lick Creek Lane)
ORGANIZER;CN="Diamond Bethea":MAILTO:dbethea@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Classes & Lectures, Health & Fitness, Spanish
