SUMMARY:Pokemon Meet-up!
DESCRIPTION:Calling all Pokémon Trainers ages 4-12 years old!\n\nBring 
 your cards and meet up with other fans to show off your collection\, 
 trade*\, and talk all things Pokémon. Whether you’re a longtime 
 collector or just getting started\, this casual meetup is a fun way to 
 share your love of Pokémon and make new friends. All experience levels 
 welcome! Participants can also make Pokémon-inspired buttons as a fun side 
 activity!\n\n*Trading is optional and participant-led with 
 parental/caregiver supervision. The Library does not mediate trades\, so 
 please trade responsibly.\n\nPlease email Lauren at lwise@dconc.gov.  Thank 
 you!
