SUMMARY:Virtual Homeschool Learning Lab
DESCRIPTION: Virtual Homeschool Learning Lab is a weekly program that 
 offers engaging enrichment lessons created just for homeschoolers via Zoom. 
 Come join us each week to learn\, explore\, and connect with other 
 homeschooling families in Durham. A supply kit will be provided for the 
 program.\n\nFor any questions regarding kit pickup or accommodation needs\, 
 please reach out to Molly at mschaefer@dconc.gov.  We ask that all requests 
 be made at least three (3) business days prior to the event to ensure we 
