BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20260331T220000Z
DTEND:20260331T230000Z
DTSTAMP:20260331T000000Z
SUMMARY:Drop-In Tech Support: eBooks & Audiobooks
DESCRIPTION:\n\nStruggling to access eBooks or audiobooks? You don’t have 
 to figure it out alone. Stop by for hands-on help using free library and 
 online resources.\n\nWhen\n\n\n	Tuesdays\n	6:00–7:00 PM\n	Drop in anytime 
 during the hour.\n\n\nWhat You’ll Get Help With\n\n\n	Downloading and 
 using Libby\n	Accessing titles on hoopla\n	Finding free audiobooks on 
 LibriVox\n	Using NC LIVE eBooks and media\n	Exploring the Internet 
 Archive\n	Setting up apps on your device\n	Borrowing\, downloading\, and 
 returning titles\n	Troubleshooting common issues\n\n\nWhat to 
 Bring\n\n\n	Smartphone\n	Tablet\n	Kindle or other e-reader\n	Laptop\n	Your 
 Durham County Library card (required for most services)\n\n\nWho Should 
 Attend\n\n\n	New users who want to get started\n	Current users who are 
 stuck or frustrated\n	Anyone who wants more free reading and listening 
 options\n\n\n\n\nFor more information please contact\n\nJason: 
 jchoward@dconc.gov\n\n
