BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20260331T220000Z
DTEND:20260331T233000Z
DTSTAMP:20260331T000000Z
SUMMARY:Durham Business Listening Tour *NEW LOCATION
DESCRIPTION:Give It To The People® x Commissioner Michelle Burton x Durham 
 County Library SBC\n\nTHIS SESSION WILL BE IN ROOM 4347\n\nAs one of the 
 NC’s leading curators of business education\, professional development\, 
 and ecosystem-building experiences\, Give It To The People® knows that 
 sustainable growth starts with real conversations. This tour is designed to 
 meet business owners where they are\, understand the challenges they face\, 
 and identify how they’re accessing (or struggling to access) the 
 resources available across Durham and the Triangle.\n\nCommissioner 
 Michelle Burton brings the heart of an educator and the vision of a public 
 servant to this initiative. Together\, we are committed to being 
 intentional about listening\, truly listening\, to what Durham’s business 
 community needs to grow\, hire\, scale\, innovate\, and stay 
 competitive.\n\nEvery stop on the tour will create space for entrepreneurs 
 to share their lived experiences\, offer insight on what’s working and 
 what isn’t\, and shape future solutions that reflect the real needs of 
 our community. From new startups to established firms\, from solo 
 consultants to brick-and-mortar owners\, this tour is a chance to ensure 
 Durham’s economic ecosystem is responsive\, equitable\, and built to 
 last.\n\nAs an added benefit\, every attendee will have the opportunity to 
 join the Give It Get It Biz Membership\, the premier hub for small business 
 connectivity\, training\, events\, and ecosystem access in Durham. 
 Membership opens the door to resources\, relationships\, and opportunities 
 that help entrepreneurs navigate the region more effectively and stay 
 plugged into the support system they deserve.\n\nThis Listening Tour is a 
 commitment to building a stronger\, more connected Durham where business 
 owners feel seen\, supported\, and equipped to thrive.\n\n\n\nLet’s Give 
 It &  Get It Together. \n\nREGISTER HERE: Durham Business Listening Tour by 
 Give It To The People
LOCATION:Main Auditorium\, Main Library (300 N. Roxboro St)
ORGANIZER;CN="Ciera Williams":MAILTO:cbwilliams@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Business
UID:LibCal-14288-15969425
URL:https://durhamcountylibrary.libcal.com/event/15969425
END:VEVENT
