SUMMARY:Children's Scavenger Hunt @ North Regional Library: Earth Month!
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Earth Month this April with an eco-themed scavenger 
 hunt!\n\nVisit the Information Desk at North Regional Library to pick up a 
 scavenger hunt sheet. Then\, explore the Children's Area to find 10 hidden 
 pictures of household items to sort into recycling or trash bins.  Once 
 you've completed the hunt and filled out your sheet\, return it to the 
 Information Desk to claim a prize!
